Class MenuItem

java.lang.Object
edu.tamu.csce331.sharetea.models.MenuItem
public class MenuItem extends Object
Menu item model representing drinks and food items in the Sharetea POS system.

This class encapsulates menu item information including pricing, categorization, availability status, and descriptive details. Menu items represent the core products offered by the Sharetea store and are used throughout the system for order processing, inventory management, and customer display.

Key features:

  • Product identification and naming
  • Category-based organization and filtering
  • Pricing management and updates
  • Availability status control
  • Product description and details

Menu items support various categories such as:

  • Tea-based beverages
  • Food items and snacks
  • Seasonal specials
  • Customizable drinks
Since:
1.0

    • MenuItem

      public MenuItem(String name, String category, BigDecimal defaultPrice, String description)
      Constructs a MenuItem with specified basic information.

      This constructor is used when creating a MenuItem with known basic information. The item is automatically set as active and ready for ordering.

      Parameters:
      name - the name of the menu item
      category - the category this item belongs to
      defaultPrice - the default price for this item
      description - the description of the menu item
